  "detailed_description": "S-COPTER is a combination of an <strong>arcade game, a platformer and a bit of a puzzle game</strong>, viewed from a 2D perspective. The player’s goal is to transport all the passengers on a level to their respective landing sites.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/d52d37c28763dedcd263f1063d225e9c.poster.avif?t=1668711975\" width=474 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/d52d37c28763dedcd263f1063d225e9c.webm?t=1668711975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/d52d37c28763dedcd263f1063d225e9c.mp4?t=1668711975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To complicate things a bit, there are many obstacles on the way, which, combined with limited life and fuel, force the player to carefully plan every flight.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 levels in single-player mode, equipped with many kinds of dangers, just waiting for one wrong move,<br></li><li>20 levels in local cooperation  mode, requiring the proper planning and coordination between two players,<br></li><li>10 maps in versus mode, in which there can be only one… surviving player,<br></li><li>difficulty so high, that you will hate us forever,<br></li><li>hand drawn 2D graphics,<br></li><li>game suitable for a five minute break at work, spontaneous beer-meetings with your friends and long sessions of cursing and throwing things.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/f743717f78c8eec5fb961a299e868d5c.poster.avif?t=1668711975\" width=474 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/f743717f78c8eec5fb961a299e868d5c.webm?t=1668711975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/f743717f78c8eec5fb961a299e868d5c.mp4?t=1668711975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "S-COPTER is a combination of an <strong>arcade game, a platformer and a bit of a puzzle game</strong>, viewed from a 2D perspective. The player’s goal is to transport all the passengers on a level to their respective landing sites.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/d52d37c28763dedcd263f1063d225e9c.poster.avif?t=1668711975\" width=474 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/d52d37c28763dedcd263f1063d225e9c.webm?t=1668711975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/d52d37c28763dedcd263f1063d225e9c.mp4?t=1668711975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To complicate things a bit, there are many obstacles on the way, which, combined with limited life and fuel, force the player to carefully plan every flight.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 levels in single-player mode, equipped with many kinds of dangers, just waiting for one wrong move,<br></li><li>20 levels in local cooperation  mode, requiring the proper planning and coordination between two players,<br></li><li>10 maps in versus mode, in which there can be only one… surviving player,<br></li><li>difficulty so high, that you will hate us forever,<br></li><li>hand drawn 2D graphics,<br></li><li>game suitable for a five minute break at work, spontaneous beer-meetings with your friends and long sessions of cursing and throwing things.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/f743717f78c8eec5fb961a299e868d5c.poster.avif?t=1668711975\" width=474 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/f743717f78c8eec5fb961a299e868d5c.webm?t=1668711975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/f743717f78c8eec5fb961a299e868d5c.mp4?t=1668711975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
